    {"id":7702529671344,"title":"Lip Liner 101","handle":"lip-liner-101","description":"\u003cp class=\"p1\"\u003eRethink everything you know about lip liner. Saie hello to Lip Liner 101™, the most foolproof, confusion free, and nourishing lip liner that makes it effortless to enhance your natural lip shape. The luxuriously creamy, soft matte formula glides on smoothly for a naturally framed or fully filled look with no tugging, tightness, feathering, or dryness—all in an elegantly understated, classic wooden pencil that minimizes excess packaging. Lip Liner 101™ comes in five versatile neutral shades that stack perfectly with your favorite gloss – like Glossybounce™ – for a timeless lip combo.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePowered by Saie Science, Lip Liner 101’s formula is supercharged with Shea Butter, Jojoba Oil and Meadowfoam Oil for a comfortable, nourishing essential. Lip Liner 101 is vegan, cruelty free and safe for sensitive skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e","published_at":"2024-09-01T11:07:26-04:00","created_at":"2024-08-13T10:40:29-04:00","vendor":"Saie","type":"Finished Good","tags":["badge:new","cruelty-free","dullness","lip","lips","new","Shade Finder","Subscription","tyb","vegan","Verishop"],"price":2000,"price_min":2000,"price_max":2000,"available":true,"price_varies":false,"compare_at_price":0,"compare_at_price_min":0,"compare_at_price_max":0,"compare_at_price_varies":false,"variants":[{"id":43845224333488,"title":"Wink","option1":"Wink","option2":null,"option3":null,"sku":"02LL05A","requires_shipping":true,"taxable":true,"featured_image":{"id":34586537459888,"product_id":7702529671344,"position":7,"created_at":"2024-08-13T11:53:30-04:00","updated_at":"2025-04-26T07:17:16-04:00","alt":"wink primary","width":1080,"height":1080,"src":"\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20250428061256\/https:\/\/saiehello.com\/cdn\/shop\/files\/saie-lip-liner_0009_Saie_LipLiner101_Silo_Wink.png?v=1745666236","varia