a deeper wash of color that's never streaky or patchy. Now available in 8 shades for a wide range of complexions to find their perfect flush. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDew Blush is safe for \u003cstrong\u003esensitive skin, fragrance free, cruelty free, formulated without gluten and vegan. \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e"}
