E and Aloe Vera hydrate and nourish for dewy, moisturized, and sun-protected skin. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e"}
