<div class="product-grid-item js-product-wrapper js-grid-product " data-title="The Brush Collection" data-price="130.00" data-variant="43039144804528" data-product-handle="the-brush-collection">

  
  <script type="application/json" class="js-product-data" data-id="7441294229680" data-handle="the-brush-collection">
    {"id":7441294229680,"title":"The Brush Collection","handle":"the-brush-collection","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cmeta charset=\"utf-8\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSaie hello to the brushes that make all the difference. Watch your makeup melt in and diffuse seamlessly with our high quality, ultra-soft, cruelty-free brushes. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"www.saiehello.com\/products\/the-base-brush\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTHE BASE BRUSH\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/a\u003e -- For a flawless diffused base. Perfect for liquid foundation products. We love to pair it with \u003ca rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"www.saiehello.com\/products\/glowy-super-skin\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eGlowy Super Skin Foundation\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/a\u003e.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"www.saiehello.com\/products\/the-big-brush\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTHE BIG BRUSH\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/a\u003e -- For buffing and blending all over. Perfect for cream and balm products. We love to pair it with \u003ca rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"www.saiehello.com\/products\/glowy-super-gel-luminizer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eGlowy Super Gel\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/a\u003e, \u003ca rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"www.saiehello.com\/products\/slip-tint-tinted-moisturizer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSlip Tint\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/a\u003e and \u003ca href=\"www.saiehello.com\/products\/sun-melt\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSun Melt\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/a\u003e.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"www.saiehello.com\/products\/the-double-brush\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTHE DOUBLE BRUSH\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/a\u003e -- The small end is for precise highlight application or concealer, the large end is for sculpting and blush. Perfect for cream products. We love to pair it with \u003ca rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"www.saiehello.com\/products\/glow-sculpt\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eGlow Sculpt\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"www.saiehello.com\/products\/hydrabeam\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHydrabeam\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/a\u003e and \u003ca rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"www.saiehello.com\/products\/dew-blush\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDew Blush\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/a\u003e.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"www.saiehello.com\/products\/the-fluffy-brush\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTHE FLUFFY BRUSH\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/a\u003e -- For light, diffused application. Perfect for powder and cream products. We love to pair it with \u003ca href=\"www.saiehello.com\/products\/airset\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAirset\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/a\u003e and \u003ca rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"www.saiehello.com\/products\/dew-blush\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDew Blush\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/a\u003e.\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https:\/\/www.saiehello.com\/products\/the-powder-blush-brush\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTHE POWDER BLUSH BRU